        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老爷呀——"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我心中好一似万把钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫怀古上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "催马加鞭到柳林，"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不知坟茔何处存。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是柳林，不知莫成坟茔，现在哪里？待我下马找寻找寻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“太常寺卿莫公之墓”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫成！掌家！莫成呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见孤坟好叫人珠泪双掉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由得一阵阵哭嚎陶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "万古流芳美名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可怜你为我把命丧了"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！你是何人，来在我家坟茔啼哭呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是我家坟茔，怎么说是你家的呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分明是我家的坟茔么！你怎么前来冒认？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。看此人讲话，好似我妻傅氏。待我向前冒叫一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！你莫非是傅氏么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！你是我何人，敢叫我“傅氏”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为丈夫莫怀古在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打鬼！打鬼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何言“打鬼”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我丈夫已死多年，岂不是鬼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻休得害怕，为丈夫并不曾死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家老爷，有两处贵相。你可有么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么贵相？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家老爷，脑后有一肉枕，又有三台骨。我若一摸，便知分晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今现有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我摸来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤妻呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一见老爷来到了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由妾身泪滔滔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "妾身言来听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "雪艳妹子哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "回头便把老爷叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "蓟州堂上一旦抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "问声莫成今何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他替我一命赴阴曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "问老爷如今往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "戚贤弟有书把我邀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "如此一同齐就道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "同到蓟州走一遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是文禄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，见过你家爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见爷爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家爹爹，哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家爷爷，骑马先行；你的爹爹，挑负行李，尚在后面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。怎么还不见到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你当真要你家爹爹么？你随我来——"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这坟茔之中，就是你家爹爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说爹爹命丧了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼望坟茔泪双抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷，妾身欲将文禄孩儿，认在你我的名下，作为螟蛉义子。不知老爷，意下"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人前去问来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文禄，我欲将你，认在我二老的名下，作一螟蛉。不知你意如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此爹娘请上，受儿一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古、傅氏",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不须拜了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，你看前面，已是蓟州，你我就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "傅氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭老爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，与你母亲带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文禄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
